videos.description: Maya Moore takes a Mystics turnover and makes a pullup 3-pointer in the final seconds of the first quarter.
videos.headline: Moore channels her "Curry pullup"

videos.description: Maya Moore denies Elena Delle Donne and Sylvia Fowles lays it in at the other end to give the Lynx a 13-point lead over the Mystics at the half.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Lynx turn defense to offense to close out half) 2017/09/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lynx turn defense to offense to close out half

videos.description: Minnesota's Renee Montgomery drills her fourth 3-pointer at the buzzer of the third quarter as the Lynx continue to rout the Mystics.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Montgomery hits buzzer-beater to end the third) 2017/09/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Montgomery hits buzzer-beater to end the third
